headline: NXP and GE HealthCare Accelerate AI Innovation in Acute Care
summary: Collaboration focuses on the development of two advanced edge AI concepts in anesthesiology and neonatal care designed to help improve patient care. NXP and GE HealthCare Collaborate NXP and GE HealthCare announced a collaboration to pioneer new advancements in edge AI innovation, beginning with new anesthesia and neonatal concepts showcased at CES 2026 LAS VEGAS and CHICAGO, Jan. 06, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- NXP Semiconductors N.V. (NASDAQ: NXPI) and GE HealthCare (NASDAQ: GEHC) today announced
